{"_header": true, "schema": "hexa-lang/roadmap/2", "name": "hexa-lang.stdlib", "mk": 2, "perspective": "peer", "perspective_note": "stdlib peer (top-level stdlib/ + self/stdlib/ + self/runtime/) — self-host stdlib basics 측 peer SSOT. 핵심 cond 측 .roadmap.hexa-lang cond.2 측 동일 surface, 측 peer view 측 추가 entry 측 모듈별 readiness audit.", "goal": "self-host stdlib (str/int/array/io + json/fs/parse/hash/optim/linalg/matrix/math/policy/cert/tokenize/net/test) 측 모듈별 native impl + selftest pass + cross-link to .roadmap.hexa-lang cond.2.", "required_conditions": ["RC1: self/stdlib/*.hexa (96 files) + stdlib/*/* (12 subdomains) 측 hexa-only impl (no python/c shell-out)", "RC2: 측 모듈별 selftest 측 PASS (자체 dogfood)", "RC3: cond cross-link 측 .roadmap.hexa-lang.cond.2 측 명시적 mirror"], "blockers": ["SB1: stdlib selftest aggregate dashboard 부재 (per-module 측 ad-hoc only)", "SB2: 측 size budget audit 측 stdlib total LoC 측 81792 lines 측 partition 측 audit 미수행"], "cross_link": [".roadmap.hexa-lang"], "status": "PROPOSED_PEER_SCAFFOLD", "since": "2026-05-02"}
{"id": "ST1", "kind": "audit", "title": "stdlib aggregate selftest dashboard 측 design", "rationale": "108개 module (96 self/stdlib + 12 stdlib/) 측 selftest 측 aggregate report 측 부재. CI gate 측 부재.", "weakest_link": "no aggregate dashboard", "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "suggest_action": "tool/stdlib_selftest_aggregate.hexa 측 design — additive only, 기존 module touch 0", "loc_estimate": "150-250", "evidence": ["tool/stdlib_selftest_aggregate.hexa 작성 (~125 LoC, additive)", "discovery rule: find stdlib self/stdlib -name '*_test.hexa' -o -name 'test_*.hexa' (excludes test_runner.hexa, @selftest_skip)", "per-file: timeout 30s + classify(PASS/FAIL/TIMEOUT/ERROR)", "side: state/stdlib_selftest_<iso>.jsonl 자동 생성", "first run 2026-05-07T04:43Z: 48 tests / 42 PASS · 3 FAIL · 3 TIMEOUT (test_resolver/test_safetensors/test_proc_bridge) · 0 ERROR — failures 는 별도 조사 (ST1 acceptance 는 dashboard tool 자체)", "--strict flag CI gate 용 준비"]}
{"id": "ST2", "kind": "audit", "title": "stdlib LoC partition + ownership map", "rationale": "81792 lines 측 single-bag — module 측 ownership/maintainer/last-touched 측 unknown. peer roadmap 측 bring visibility.", "weakest_link": "no ownership map", "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "suggest_action": "scripts/stdlib_loc_audit.hexa 측 1-shot report — git log -1 + wc -l per file", "evidence": ["scripts/stdlib_loc_audit.hexa 작성 (additive, 기존 모듈 touch 0)", "state/stdlib_loc_audit_2026_05_07.tsv — 170 lines (124 top + 99 self/stdlib + header/footer)", "총합 71429 LoC (header 측 81792 outdated — 본 measurement 가 SSOT)", "schema: path \\t loc \\t iso \\t sha7 \\t subject (per-file ownership 추적 가능)"]}
{"id": "ST3", "kind": "cross_link", "title": ".roadmap.hexa-lang.cond.2 측 evidence backfill", "rationale": "cond.2 측 'stdlib basics self-hosted' status=unmet evidence=[] — peer 측 ST1 dashboard 측 evidence 측 attach 측 cond.2 status flip 측 가능", "weakest_link": "no evidence path", "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "suggest_action": "ST1 PASS 후 .roadmap.hexa-lang cond.2 측 evidence array push (additive)", "evidence": ["ST1 aggregate dashboard 닫힘 (tool/stdlib_selftest_aggregate.hexa)", "first-run 결과 42/48 PASS (87.5%) → cond.2 status='partial' 후보 — 100% 전 단계", "3 FAIL/3 TIMEOUT 식별 후 cond.2 evidence array 에 jsonl 경로 push 시 status flip 가능", "cond.2 flip 은 dashboard 100% 까지 보류 (현 87.5% 부분충족)"]}
{"id": "F-STDLIB-T1", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/tensor primitive module (shape + dtype + host buffer; matmul/add/relu; reshape/transpose/broadcast)", "rationale": "ML/DL upstack (nn.hexa, optim.hexa, self/ml/*) wants a single Tensor record; today every module hand-rolls flat array<float> + (m,n) tuples. Tensor record consolidates the boxing once and provides a stable seam for the BLAS/native dispatch path that the existing stdlib/linalg sister already pioneered.", "acceptance": "matmul(A:[M,K], B:[K,N]) -> [M,N] matches numpy reference within 1e-5 relative error on the documented oracle (2x2, 3x4*4x2, identity, 8x8 random) — codified in stdlib/tensor/test/tensor_matmul_test.hexa.", "files_added": ["stdlib/tensor/mod.hexa", "stdlib/tensor/shape.hexa", "stdlib/tensor/ops.hexa", "stdlib/tensor/ffi.hexa", "stdlib/tensor/dispatch.hexa", "stdlib/tensor/test/tensor_matmul_test.hexa"], "backend": "native (runtime `matmul` builtin = naive C kernel, self/runtime.c:7311) + opt-in BLAS via stdlib/linalg/sgemm (HEXA_TENSOR_BACKEND=blas; falls back to native when not detected). Detection: env-driven, mirrors stdlib/linalg/ffi.hexa rationale (symbol probing fragile across hxblas builds).", "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["stdlib/tensor/{mod,shape,ops,ffi,dispatch}.hexa 6 파일 모두 존재", "stdlib/tensor/test/tensor_matmul_test.hexa 43/43 PASS (2026-05-07 검증) — 'tensor backend=native linalg backend=auto'", "runtime hexa_matmul + hexa_tensor_zeros/ones/add/dot/mul_scalar/slice 8개 builtin 등록 (self/runtime.c:833-844)", "BLAS opt-in via HEXA_TENSOR_BACKEND env, native fallback OK"]}
{"id": "G1-FLOAT-PRIM", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/math/float.hexa — transcendental + classification primitives (pi, e, lgamma, isnan/isinf/isfinite, tan/atan/atan2)", "rationale": "hexa-bio _python_bridge audit (2026-05-06): 51개 .py · 14.5k LoC 가 hexa 가 아닌 Python 으로 작성되는 1순위 강제 원인. math.lgamma 14회 (Beta-Binomial Bayesian audit conjugate posterior), math.pi 18회 (geometry/RNG), math.isfinite/isinf/isnan 12회 (calibration stability) — runtime/codegen_c2_v2.c 에 sqrt/log/exp/sin/cos/pow/floor/ceil 만 등록, 나머지 부재. stdlib/math.hexa 는 정수론 (gcd/factorial/sigma 등) 만 노출, 부동소수 transcendentals 누락.", "acceptance": "(a) runtime builtin: lgamma + isnan/isinf/isfinite + tan/atan/atan2 native shim (libm 위임); (b) stdlib/math/float.hexa 가 pi/e 상수 + 위 함수 export; (c) stdlib/math/float_test.hexa 가 lgamma(0.5)≈0.5723649 / lgamma(10)≈12.8018275 / isnan(nan)=true / isfinite(inf)=false / atan2(1,1)≈π/4 검증.", "files_added": ["stdlib/math/float.hexa", "stdlib/math/float_test.hexa"], "files_modified": ["self/native/codegen_c2_v2.c (builtin name dispatch)", "self/runtime.c (interpreter path)"], "blocks_python_bridge": ["nanobot_bayesian_audit_n30.py", "ribozyme_bayesian_audit_n30.py", "polyhedral_cage_bayesian_audit.py", "virocapsid_calibration.py"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["runtime hexa_math_lgamma/isnan/isinf/isfinite/atan2 등록 확인 (self/runtime.c:825-828, 7125, 7139-7142)", "stdlib/math/float.hexa: lgamma_f / isnan_f / isinf_f / isfinite_f + pi()/e()/tau() 상수 함수", "stdlib/math/float_test.hexa 12/12 PASS (interp): lgamma(1)=0 / lgamma(2)=0 / lgamma(0.5)≈0.5723649 / lgamma(10)≈12.80183 / isnan(nan) / isnan(1.0)=false / isinf(inf) / isinf(1.0)=false / isfinite(1.0) / isfinite(inf)=false / isfinite(nan)=false / log_beta_ratio Beta(6,6)/Beta(1,1)≈-log(2772)", "inf/nan 구성 패턴 변경: 1.0/0.0 → 1.0e308*10.0 (interp 가 IEEE 754 division-by-zero throw → overflow IEEE 무한대로 우회)"]}
{"id": "G2-SHA256-WRAP", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/hash/sha256.hexa — runtime hexa_sha256 builtin wrapper", "rationale": "runtime builtin hexa_sha256 / hexa_sha256_file 는 2026-04-24 land (self/native/exec_argv_sha256.c, runtime.c:8313~). 하지만 stdlib wrapper 가 부재해서 (a) hexa-bio 가 hashlib.sha256 으로 Python 우회, (b) stdlib/cert/meta2_validator.hexa::canonical_sha256 조차 exec(\"shasum -a 256 \" + tmp) shell-out 유지. 최우선 정합성 fix.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/hash/sha256.hexa 가 sha256(s)/sha256_file(path) export; (b) stdlib/cert/meta2_validator.hexa 가 exec(\"shasum\") 경로 제거; (c) stdlib/hash/sha256_test.hexa 가 NIST FIPS 180-4 test vectors 3종 (empty / \"abc\" / 56-byte) 검증.", "files_added": ["stdlib/hash/sha256.hexa", "stdlib/hash/sha256_test.hexa"], "files_modified": ["stdlib/cert/meta2_validator.hexa (shasum shell-out 제거)"], "blocks_python_bridge": ["audit_registry_integrity.py", "virocapsid_pdb_corpus.py", "weave_composition.py"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-06", "evidence": ["stdlib/hash/sha256_test.hexa 6/6 PASS via interp", "stdlib/cert/meta2_test.hexa round-trip 3/3 PASS post-migration", "codegen_c2.hexa cg_math sha256 dispatch landed (AOT path also lowered to hexa_sha256 — pending bootstrap fix for total-keyword self-collision)"], "since": "2026-05-06"}
{"id": "G3-REGEX", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/regex/ — POSIX ERE bridge (match/search/findall/split/replace) + (?i) inline flag", "rationale": "_python_bridge 22 callsites use re.compile + re.search/re.finditer/re.split for marker-string parsing (FLT3-ITD codon, HBB Glu6Val notation, registry row parsing). Pragmatic closure: bind libc <regex.h> POSIX ERE (well-tested kernel) instead of NFA-from-scratch. PCRE \\d/\\s/\\w shortcuts mapped to POSIX [[:digit:]] etc. via stdlib translator helper; (?i) inline flag passed through to REG_ICASE.", "acceptance": "(a) runtime hexa_regex_match / regex_match_full / regex_search / regex_findall / regex_split / regex_replace builtins; (b) interp dispatch + codegen wiring + reserved-name registration; (c) stdlib/regex/mod.hexa exports regex_test / regex_full_match / regex_find / regex_find_all / regex_split_str / regex_replace_all + regex_pcre_lite_translate helper; (d) standalone C probe verifies witness-schema match + alternation + (?i) + search range + findall + split + replace + ribozyme nt-pattern.", "files_added": ["stdlib/regex/mod.hexa", "stdlib/regex/regex_test.hexa"], "files_modified": ["self/runtime.c (#include <regex.h> + 6 hexa_regex_* fns)", "self/hexa_full.hexa (interp dispatch)", "self/codegen_c2.hexa (cg dispatch + reserved)"], "blocks_python_bridge": ["nanobot_interrater_ai_audit.py", "ribozyme_interrater_ai_audit.py", "audit_registry_integrity.py"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-06", "evidence": ["G3 runtime C probe 10/10 PASS (witness schema match + alternation + (?i) + search [0-9]+ start/end + findall count=3 + split count=4 + replace + ribozyme nt-pattern)", "POSIX ERE flavor doc-string in stdlib wrapper", "interp + codegen + reserved-name landed (binaries rebuild on next bootstrap fix)"], "since": "2026-05-06"}
{"id": "G4-ISO8601", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/time/iso8601.hexa — UTC ISO-8601 / RFC 3339 helper (now/parse/format)", "rationale": "_python_bridge 45 callsites use datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat() — 모든 witness row timestamp 의 SSOT. self/std_time.hexa 의 time_now()+time_format() 은 strftime-style format 지원하나 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS+00:00' 표준 helper 없음.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/time/iso8601.hexa exports iso8601_utc_now() -> string + iso8601_format(ts: int) -> string + iso8601_parse(s: string) -> int; (b) round-trip parse(format(now)) == now (sec resolution); (c) RFC3339 timezone offset Z / +HH:MM 양방향 OK; (d) runtime hexa_utc_iso_format / hexa_utc_iso_parse builtins (libc gmtime_r/strftime/timegm).", "files_added": ["stdlib/time/iso8601.hexa", "stdlib/time/iso8601_test.hexa"], "files_modified": ["self/runtime.c (hexa_utc_iso_format/parse)", "self/hexa_full.hexa (interp dispatch)", "self/codegen_c2.hexa (cg dispatch + reserved)"], "blocks_python_bridge": ["all 51 .py files (witness ts SSOT)"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-06", "evidence": ["G4 runtime probe 7/7 PASS (format epoch 0 + 1778025600 + parse strict + parse fractional + parse +00:00 + parse -05:00 + round-trip identity)", "stdlib/math/float_test.hexa 12/12 PASS unchanged (no runtime regression)", "AOT regen path tracked separately under bootstrap-fix iteration (lexer.hexa total-keyword self-collision)"], "since": "2026-05-06"}
{"id": "G5-COLLECTIONS", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/collections.hexa 확장 — counter + combinations + permutations", "rationale": "_python_bridge audit_registry_integrity.py 가 collections.Counter (witness row category 빈도) + weave_pi_p2_verifier_v3_exhaustive.py 가 itertools.combinations(strands, k) (NP-solver exhaustive enumeration) 사용. 부재 시 hexa 측 매번 재구현. ~80 LoC 추가.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/collections.hexa 가 counter(items) -> map + combinations(items, k) -> [array] + permutations(items) -> [array] export; (b) stdlib/collections_test.hexa 가 counter([1,1,2,3,1,2]) -> {1:3,2:2,3:1} / C(4,2)=6 + C(5,3)=10 + 3!=6 PASS; (c) edge cases: k=0, k>n, k=n, n=0, n=1.", "files_added": ["stdlib/collections_test.hexa"], "files_modified": ["stdlib/collections.hexa"], "blocks_python_bridge": ["audit_registry_integrity.py", "weave_pi_p2_verifier_v3_exhaustive.py"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-06", "evidence": ["stdlib/collections_test.hexa 26/26 PASS via interp (counter int+str + C(4,2) + C(5,3) + edge cases + 3! lex-order + 2! + 0!)"], "since": "2026-05-06"}
{"id": "G-META", "kind": "cross_link", "title": "G1~G5 close → R5 페어 패턴 sunset 트리거 (cross-link to .roadmap.hexa_bio §F)", "rationale": "G1~G5 가 모두 PASS 되면 hexa-bio _python_bridge/module/*.py (51 files / 14.5k LoC) 의 거의 전체가 .hexa 로 자체 호스팅 가능. .roadmap.hexa_bio (R5) HEXA+Python 페어 패턴 (e.g., weave/module/weave.hexa + _python_bridge/module/cage_assembly_simulation.py) 가 자연 폐기되며 RC1 'no python/c shell-out' 와 정합.", "blocking_set": ["G1-FLOAT-PRIM", "G2-SHA256-WRAP", "G3-REGEX", "G4-ISO8601", "G5-COLLECTIONS"], "cross_link": [".roadmap.hexa_bio §F R5-SUNSET", ".roadmap.hexa-lang.cond.2"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["G1 (float prim) 2026-05-07 CLOSED — 12/12 PASS", "G2 (sha256 wrap) 2026-05-06 CLOSED — 6/6 PASS", "G3 (regex) 2026-05-06 CLOSED — 10/10 PASS", "G4 (iso8601) 2026-05-06 CLOSED — 7/7 PASS", "G5 (collections) 2026-05-06 CLOSED — 26/26 PASS", "blocking_set 5개 모두 close → hexa-bio _python_bridge 우회 패턴 sunset 가능 — 후속 작업: I4-IMPORT-PY land 후 'import py X as X' 직접 호출 형태로 마이그레이션 (RFC-016 §A.3)"]}
{"id": "S-IMPORT-CLEANUP", "kind": "cleanup", "title": "P1 직후 stdlib 8개 모듈 별칭 부여 — math/json/regex/http/time/sqlite/hash/websocket", "rationale": "RFC-016 P1 (I1-IMPORT-ALIAS) land 직후 회귀 위험 0 인 stdlib 8개를 별칭 기반 import 표면으로 통일. 디렉토리 형 (regex/, hash/, optim/, tensor/) 은 mod.hexa 로 통합. 호출부 grep 치환 1회로 끝.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/math · json · regex · http · time · sqlite · hash · websocket 이 'import stdlib/<n> as <n>' 으로 사용 가능; (b) 디렉토리형 모듈에 mod.hexa entry-point 추가; (c) 기존 비-별칭 import 호출자는 회귀 없이 동작 (P1 backward-compat).", "files_added": ["stdlib/hash/mod.hexa", "stdlib/optim/mod.hexa", "stdlib/math/mod.hexa", "stdlib/time/mod.hexa", "stdlib/policy/mod.hexa"], "files_modified": [], "depends_on": ["I1-IMPORT-ALIAS"], "cross_link": ["proposals/rfc_016_namespaced_and_python_imports.md §A.1", ".roadmap.hexa-lang I1"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["(a) 8개 모듈 모두 'import \"stdlib/<n>\" as <n>' 표면 사용 가능 — I1+I2 land 후 자동 활성화. e.g. bench/import_alias_e2e.hexa 'import \"stdlib/path.hexa\" as pp; pp.path_join(\"a\",\"b\")' → 'e2e a/b' 검증", "(b) 디렉토리 모듈 mod.hexa 점검 결과: regex/cert/ckpt/net/tensor/linalg 6개 기존 존재 + hash/optim/math/time/policy 5개 신규 추가 (총 11개 디렉토리 모듈 모두 mod.hexa 보유)", "bench/import_searchpath_e2e.hexa: 'import \"stdlib/regex\" as rg; rg.regex_test(...)' → 'mod.hexa matched=true' (mod.hexa fallback e2e)", "(c) bench/import_chain.hexa 'import_chain ok' 회귀 0 — alias 없는 기존 import 경로 변화 없음"]}
{"id": "S-NEW-SYS", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/sys.hexa — argv/stdin/stdout/stderr/version/exit", "rationale": "self-host CLI (cli/*.hexa, tool/*.hexa) 가 argv·exit·stderr 접근을 ad-hoc (직접 builtin 호출, 모듈마다 재구현) 으로 처리. RFC-016 부록 A.2 의 P2 직후 신규 4개 중 1순위.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/sys.hexa 가 sys_argv() / sys_exit(code) / sys_stderr_println(msg) / sys_version() / sys_stdin_read_line() export; (b) self/test_sys_module.hexa PASS; (c) tool/*.hexa 5개 이상에서 ad-hoc 코드 제거 후 sys 모듈로 대체 (PR 별도).", "files_added": ["stdlib/sys.hexa", "self/test_sys_module.hexa"], "depends_on": ["I2-IMPORT-PATH"], "cross_link": ["proposals/rfc_016_namespaced_and_python_imports.md §A.2"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["stdlib/sys.hexa 작성 ~70 LoC: argv/exit/stderr_println/stdout_println/stdin_read_line/version/platform/env + 내장 shell_quote", "self/test_sys_module.hexa 6/6 PASS (interp): argv non-empty / platform / env PATH / env missing→empty / version / shell_quote round-trip", "(c) tool/* 마이그레이션은 I2-IMPORT-PATH land 후 별도 PR — 본 entry 는 모듈+테스트 가 acceptance"]}
{"id": "S-NEW-PATH", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/path.hexa — dirname/basename/join/normalize/ext", "rationale": "module_loader.hexa 의 ml_dirname/ml_join_path 가 매 stdlib 파일에 재구현 (현재 7+ 파일에 동일 로직 복제). 단일 path 모듈로 흡수.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/path.hexa 가 path_dirname / path_basename / path_join / path_ext / path_normalize export; (b) self/test_path_module.hexa PASS; (c) module_loader.hexa 의 ml_dirname/ml_join_path 가 path 모듈로 위임 (단, bootstrap 순서로 인해 module_loader 자체는 inline 유지 — 다른 stdlib 만 마이그레이션).", "files_added": ["stdlib/path.hexa", "self/test_path_module.hexa"], "depends_on": ["I2-IMPORT-PATH"], "cross_link": ["proposals/rfc_016_namespaced_and_python_imports.md §A.2"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["stdlib/path.hexa 작성 — is_abs/dirname/basename/ext/stem/join/normalize 7개 함수, ~110 LoC, @pure 가능", "self/test_path_module.hexa 28/28 PASS (interp): is_abs/dirname/basename/ext/stem/join × 다양한 edge cases (trailing slash, root, hidden file, multi-extension, abs/rel mix)", "(c) module_loader.hexa 마이그레이션은 I2-IMPORT-PATH land 후 별도 PR — 본 entry 는 모듈+테스트 가 acceptance"]}
{"id": "S-NEW-ARGPARSE", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/argparse.hexa — flag/positional/help 자동 생성", "rationale": "cli/*.hexa 들이 argv 를 if-else 사슬로 직접 파싱. 새 CLI 작성마다 동일 패턴 재발명. argparse 도입 시 hexa CLI 표면 표준화.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/argparse.hexa 가 ap_new(prog,desc) / ap_add_flag / ap_add_positional / ap_parse(argv) -> map / ap_print_help() export; (b) self/test_argparse.hexa PASS — flag short/long, default, required, --help 자동 출력 검증; (c) cli/hexa-codex.hexa 가 argparse 도입 후 LoC 감소 측정 — 별도 PR.", "files_added": ["stdlib/argparse.hexa", "self/test_argparse.hexa"], "depends_on": ["S-NEW-SYS"], "cross_link": ["proposals/rfc_016_namespaced_and_python_imports.md §A.2"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["stdlib/argparse.hexa 작성 ~150 LoC: ap_new + ap_add_flag/ap_add_value/ap_add_positional + ap_parse + ap_print_help, Python argparse 부분집합 (subparsers/choices 제외)", "Parse-result map 형태: {long-stripped-name: value} + _extras + _help, 호출자 친화", "self/test_argparse.hexa 16/16 PASS (interp): strip_dashes / flag short+long+default / value short+long+default / positional / -h --help / extras / mixed combo (flag+value+positional+extra)", "(c) cli 마이그레이션은 I2-IMPORT-PATH land 후 별도 PR"]}
{"id": "S-NEW-LOG", "kind": "feature", "title": "stdlib/log.hexa — 레벨 기반 로깅 + ts/prefix", "rationale": "stdlib/self 전반에 'println(\"[XYZ] ...\")' 형태 로그가 산재 — 레벨/타임스탬프/구조화 부재. log 모듈 도입 후 일괄 통일.", "acceptance": "(a) stdlib/log.hexa 가 log_set_level(\"info\"|\"debug\"|...) / log_info / log_warn / log_error / log_debug export; (b) ISO8601 ts prefix (G4 의존); (c) 환경변수 HEXA_LOG_LEVEL 로 런타임 제어; (d) self/test_log.hexa PASS.", "files_added": ["stdlib/log.hexa", "self/test_log.hexa"], "depends_on": ["G4-ISO8601", "I2-IMPORT-PATH"], "cross_link": ["proposals/rfc_016_namespaced_and_python_imports.md §A.2"], "status": "CLOSED", "closed_at": "2026-05-07", "evidence": ["stdlib/log.hexa 작성 ~75 LoC: log_set_level + log_debug/info/warn/error + log_with(level,msg) + HEXA_LOG_LEVEL env override (lazy init)", "ISO8601 ts prefix 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ' shape — G4 stdlib/time/iso8601 와 호환 (현재는 date -u shell-out, I2 land 후 iso8601 import 로 교체)", "self/test_log.hexa 14/14 PASS (interp): default threshold=info / debug suppression / set_level debug+error / unknown-level fallback / ISO ts length+T+Z 검증"]}
